Comment: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.18,main-JP,,0,0,0,,OP-before
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.18,0:00:03.10,main-JP,SISTER,0,0,0,,お慶び申し上げます
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.19,0:00:07.19,main-JP,SISTER,0,0,0,,英雄　フラム・アプリコット様
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.90,0:00:11.94,main-JP,SISTER,0,0,0,,方様は創造神　オリジン様に選ばれました
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.58,main-JP,KIDS,0,0,0,,みんな　頑張れ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.64,main-JP,JEAN,0,0,0,,お前ごときが
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.94,main-JP,JEAN,0,0,0,,魔王に勝てると思うな
Comment: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:46.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:59.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:01.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:04.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:06.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:11.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:16.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:21.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:31.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:36.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:39.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:46.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:51.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:53.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Aren't you? 明鏡探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
